# rosetta-frida pre-commit hook — the FAST half.
#
# Runs typecheck + lint + format:check. The full test suite + 100%
# coverage gate runs in pre-push (and again in CI), so this hook only
# blocks commits on the static-analysis checks.
#
# Bypass with `git commit --no-verify` if you need to commit WIP.
npm run verify:fast
